{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_05_01",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 05 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、渚。久しぶりのオフなのに\nどうして私達は部屋にこもって勉強してるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Nagisa. It's a rare day off‚ but\nWhy are we cooped up in our room studying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.4666666667,
      "endTime": 9.781428909399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.9814290047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ期末試験だからだよ\n琴乃ちゃん、ちゃんとテスト勉強してた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because the final exams are coming up soon‚ Kotono.\nKotono-chan‚ have you been studying properly for the tests?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9814290047,
      "endTime": 16.5411340713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.727800719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "う……そ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… w-well‚ that's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.727800719,
      "endTime": 20.2829481761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.4829481999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが赤点なんて格好つかないよ？\nテスト前くらいはしっかり勉強しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An idol failing would be a bad look‚ you know?\nLet's study hard at least before the tests.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4829481999,
      "endTime": 27.3346487918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.5346486965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\nテストなんてこの世からなくなればいいのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sigh…\nI wish tests would just disappear from the world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5346486965,
      "endTime": 33.1040364185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.2973696469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……琴乃ちゃんのこんな気弱な姿\n他のメンバーには見せられないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "chuckles… Kotono‚ seeing you so timid like this…\nI can't let the other members see it‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2973696469,
      "endTime": 40.2568483112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.4435149589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "言われなくても、渚以外にはこんな姿見せないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to tell me. I wouldn't show this side of me to anyone but you‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4435149589,
      "endTime": 45.312086240300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.4587546585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私には見られてもいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay for me to see it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4587546585,
      "endTime": 47.707303452299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.8939700522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "今更でしょ。渚には私の恥ずかしい姿を\n沢山見られてるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not like you haven't seen it before. You've seen so many embarrassing sides of me‚ Nagisa.\nYou've seen them all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8939700522,
      "endTime": 54.8961470999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.1028138237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、渚ならどんな私を見ても\nずっと友達でいてくれるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Besides‚ Nagisa‚ no matter what side of me you see…\nYou'll always be my friend‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1028138237,
      "endTime": 63.3042196349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.4908862826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、それは間違いないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "chuckles Of course‚ that's for sure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4908862826,
      "endTime": 66.7278929946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.9412262754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、この辺で休憩にしようか\n実は琴乃ちゃんに聞きたいことがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ shall we take a break around here?\nActually‚ there's something I want to ask you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9412262754,
      "endTime": 74.0578928785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.2645593163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私に聞きたいこと？　何かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something you want to ask me? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2645593163,
      "endTime": 78.64186081849999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "この間、沙季ちゃんに聞かれて\n私達が出会った時の話をしたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ Saki asked me something.\nI told her the story of how we met‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8418609139,
      "endTime": 84.1956702706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.4223332242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、話しながら思ったんだ\n琴乃ちゃんの目に私はどんな風に映ってたんだろうって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ as I was telling the story‚ I thought…\nI wondered how I looked in your eyes‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4223332242,
      "endTime": 92.8893854933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "だから今度は、琴乃ちゃんの目から見た\n昔の話を聞いてみたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this time‚ I want to hear… from your point of view‚ Kotono…\n…the story of the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0960521218,
      "endTime": 98.6302473542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.8369140781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "別に構わないけど……\n面白い話なんて何もないわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind‚ but…\nThere's nothing interesting to tell‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8369140781,
      "endTime": 104.70011121399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9833351135
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1401105718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "（私は小さい頃から人付き合いが苦手で）\n（いつもお姉ちゃんとばかり遊んでた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ever since I was little‚ I was bad at socializing.）\n（I always just played with my sister.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9401105718,
      "endTime": 113.4436480359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんはいつも私の手を引っ張って）\n（いろんな景色を見せてくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My sister always pulled me along by the hand.）\n（She showed me all kinds of scenery.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7303133484,
      "endTime": 119.1062544342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "（明るくて優しいお姉ちゃんは私の憧れで）\n（私の世界の全てだった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My bright and kind sister was my idol‚）\n（She was everything in my world…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4729184623,
      "endTime": 126.729970693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9534070487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-03.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんはアイドルになるから、琴乃も応援してね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your sister is going to become an idol‚ so please cheer me on‚ Kotono!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9699699556,
      "endTime": 133.95139695749998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3847297822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "（私が中学一年生の時）\n（お姉ちゃんは突然そんなことを言い出した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When I was in the first year of middle school）\n（My sister suddenly said something like that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1847297822,
      "endTime": 142.565663353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
